CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `warehouse_orders` (`id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`item_name_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`item_manufacturer_id` tinyint(3) DEFAULT NULL,`item_qty` mediumint(7) DEFAULT NULL,`item_die_date` date DEFAULT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `warehouse_settings` (`id` mediumint(7) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`warehouse_id` smallint(5) DEFAULT NULL,`division_id` smallint(5) DEFAULT NULL,`add_date` datetime DEFAULT current_timestamp(),PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `warehouse_supply` (`id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`uniq_key` char(25) DEFAULT NULL,`is_order` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`add_date` datetime DEFAULT current_timestamp(),`supply_date` date DEFAULT NULL,`completed` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,`completed_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `warehouse_supply_items` (`id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`uniq_key` char(25) DEFAULT NULL,`item_name_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`item_manufacturer_id` tinyint(3) DEFAULT NULL,`item_supplier_id` smallint(5) DEFAULT NULL,`item_qty` mediumint(7) DEFAULT NULL,`item_cost` decimal(65,1) DEFAULT 0.0,`item_price` decimal(65,1) DEFAULT 0.0,`item_faktura` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,`item_die_date` date DEFAULT current_timestamp(),PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `warehouses` (`id` smallint(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`is_active` tinyint(1) DEFAULT 1,`name` char(255) DEFAULT NULL,`parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,`level` longtext DEFAULT NULL,`division` longtext DEFAULT NULL,`add_date` datetime DEFAULT current_timestamp(),PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
